15:15.740 --> 15:17.970
if you think
I'm working from bias.

15:18.010 --> 15:18.999
I'll be in touch.

15:19.050 --> 15:20.017
And you'll read our complaint?

15:20.050 --> 15:22.075
Oh, yes. I have it right here.

15:22.120 --> 15:24.509
