to my next meeting.

15:24.550 --> 15:26.381
ALICIA:
Hello?

15:26.420 --> 15:27.956
Oh, hi.

15:27.990 --> 15:30.322
I just saw
you had to run off, so, I...

15:30.360 --> 15:31.987
Oh, my gosh.

15:32.030 --> 15:33.349
